### Enable APM for MongoDB Instrumentation

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

This configuration enables Application Performance Monitoring (APM) for MongoDB instrumentation by setting `client.monitorCommands` to `true`. This is necessary for full support of v4 of the `mongodb` driver.

```javascript
client.monitorCommands = true;
```

