### Configure Unresolved Promise Cleanup Feature Flag

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

This snippet shows how to disable the `unresolved_promise_cleanup` feature flag, which can improve agent performance in applications with many promises. Disabling this flag may lead to memory leaks if promises are not properly resolved.

```javascript
feature_flag.unresolved_promise_cleanup: false
```

```bash
NEW_RELIC_FEATURE_FLAG_UNRESOLVED_PROMISE_CLEANUP=false
```

