### Enable New Promise Tracking for Reduced Overhead

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

This snippet shows how to enable the 'new_promise_tracking' feature flag in the New Relic agent configuration. This flag aims to reduce overhead associated with promise handling, potentially improving performance by optimizing segment cleanup. It's recommended to test your application with this flag to verify overhead reduction and data capture.

```javascript
module.exports = {
  feature_flag: {
    new_promise_tracking: true
  }
};
```

