### Set Ignore Transaction API - Node.js

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

Adds the `setIgnoreTransaction` API call to explicitly control which transactions should be ignored by the New Relic agent. This is useful for excluding specific routes or custom logic, such as favicon rendering, from performance monitoring.

```javascript
